				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Word of Darkness</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=34716"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
