					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Word of Darkness.<BR>
<BR>
I am not sure exactly what this item is yet, but the info i have at this point is this<BR>
<BR>
Shadow book(rom shadowmen)<BR>
book of Darkness (erudites in lake rathe)<BR>
book of Frost ( ice goblins in permafrost)<BR>
300 Gold pieces.<BR>
<BR>
off to permafrost very soon since i like that place the most.  will give updates as i get it.<BR>
<BR>
Zerg Sentient<BR>
lvl 30 Necro<BR>
Bertoxxoulus
