				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Woot!  They did indeed fix it.  Cyanelle cons green to me at 40.  Eldreth wasn't around so I figured no prob.  I was afraid she was going to charm my pet so I feared her and rooted her pet, then vos.  She ran too fast to cast anything else on her.  Fear broke and she came running back at me.  She cast some weak dd spell on me and then came and attacked me hand to hand, punching for 115 damage!  I don't get how a green caster can do that kinda damage.  She got me down to one bub of health that way before I feigned.<BR>
<BR>
Back at full health I brought out my pet, sent it on her pet as I darknessed her, then feared her.  Cast VoS and then started nuking her just to make sure.  She went down after 3 or so nukes, so I'd guess she has 500-700 hp.  I don't know if she's able to charm anymore, she didn't seem to try.  My pet took her pet out easily.  I had to kill her twice before she dropped the book of darkness.  Now I'm off to Permafrost.  Hope it won't be a big pain.
